1. *Pravde* nikada nije bilo u ovom sudu. (There was never any *justice* in this court.)
2. Ova država se zalaže za zaštitu *pravde*. (This state advocates for the protection of *justice*.)
3. Da bi postigli *pravdu*, svi moraju poštovati zakone. (In order to achieve *justice*, everyone must respect the laws.)
4. Sudija je odlučio u korist *pravde*. (The judge ruled in favor of *justice*.)
5. Mnogi ljudi traže *pravdu* zbog zlostavljanja. (Many people seek *justice* for abuse.)
6. Njegovo ime je postalo sinonim za *pravdu* i poštenje. (His name has become synonymous with *justice* and honesty.)
7. Ovo je kršenje *pravde* i ljudskih prava. (This is a violation of *justice* and human rights.)
8. Ona je uvijek bila borac za *pravdu*. (She has always been a fighter for *justice*.)
9. Mnogi su izgubili nadu u *pravdu* nakon tog slučaja. (Many have lost hope in *justice* after that case.)
10. Bez *pravde* nema slobode ni mira. (Without *justice* there is no freedom or peace.)